ChangeLog for orbit
===============================

Version 2.11 - 2014-05-05 (BP)
-------------

- Fixed bug in test harness that had hard linked local path embedded. 

Version 2.10 - 2014-04-25 (BP)
-------------

- Allows time ranges outside exposures (within full orbit).
- Added celestial to geocentric solar ecliptic conversion. 
- Added useobsid boolean to select keywords to remove from output file. 
- Fixed test harness (csh script failed on some systems). 
- Bug fixes and SPR closures. 

Version 2.9 - 2002-07-26 (BP)
-------------

- Uploaded as 2.9 for consistency
	
Version 2.8.1 - 2002-07-25 (BP)
-------------

- Updated build for param-2.5.
- Updated DEPEND file.
	
Version 2.8 - 2001-07-26 (BP)
-------------

- Fixed test harness
- Fixed array bug
- Added new odf for test
	
Version 2.7 - 2001-06-06 (BP)
-------------

- Fixed bug in layout file.
- Checked task on new data.	
- Updated DEPEND file.
- New ODF Orbit file in test harness.	
	
Version 2.6.1 - 2000-11-30 (BP)
-------------

- Fixed date format in docs and ChangeLog.
- Added info file to config/Makefile.	
	
Version 2.6 - 2000-11-16 (BP)
-------------

- Fixed OAL call.
- Corrected doc link error and ChangeLog.	
	
Version 2.5.2 - 2000-07-01 (GV/SOC)
-------------
	+ modify DEPEND to contan dal-1.121 or cannot be built on releasetrack.

Version 2.5.1 -- 2000-06-16 (BP)
----------------------

- Updated DEPEND file.	
- Added task info file (SSC-SPR-1803).
- Fixed broken doc links (SSC-SPR-1831).
	
Version 2.5 -- 2000-05-12 (BP)
----------------------

- Fixed 'env' bug in doc file orbit_description.tex
	
Version 2.4 -- 2000-05-12 (BP)
----------------------

- Removed Oal_expandFileName following OAL 3.52 release, which
  made it unnecessary.
- Removed infile from parameter list; not necessary for OAL calls.
- Modified test harness.	
	
Version 2.3 -- 2000-04-27 (BP)
----------------------

- Added macros for warnings and errors to doc.
- Added orbit.info file.
- Bug fix in test harness.

Version 2.2 -- 2000-04-07 (BP)
----------------------

- added layout file
- SAS_ODF must now be set.	

Version 2.1 -- 2000-03-15 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Changed CITE to bibitems in doc.
	
Version 2.0 -- 2000-03-06 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Bug Fixes, 'real' OAL calls (not dummy), reads actual
  'predicted' orbit file, test harness bug fix, first version
  to actually read *POS.ASC and *SUM.ASC file from odf and 
  create FITS orbit file not 'calculated'.
	
Version 1.7 -- 2000-02-12 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Bug Fixes (incl Linux problems)
	
Version 1.6 -- 1999-12-12 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Added tests to orbit_test

Version 1.5 -- 1999-08-20 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Changed parameter selectime to selecttimes	

Version 1.4 -- 1999-08-19 (BP)
----------------------
	
- Implemented UL's change to
  OAL_getPosition. Now called with
  function return instead of checking
  values of pos and vel.	
	
Version 1.3 -- 1999-08-05 (BP)
----------------------

- Added selecttime parameter
- bug fixes and error checking	
	
Version 1.2 -- 1999-07-22 (BP)
----------------------

- Changed ODF(XMM,RECONSTRUCTED_ORBIT) filename
  designation in orbit_test to ODF(XMM,RECON)
  because it didn't equal the Xmm.h expected value.
- Now issues warning if starttime=0. and endtime=0.
  then defaults to odfinfo%observationStartTime and
  odfinfo%observationEndTime
	
Version 1.1 -- 1999-07-07 (BP)
----------------------

- Corrected dependency errors.


Version 1.0 -- 1999-07-05 (BP)
----------------------

- Approved working version. Includes velocity vectors
  from OAL_getPosition	
- Includes checkorbit test program	
- Allows OAL expandFilename input set convension.
	
Version 0.2 -- 1999-06-29 (BP)
----------------------

- draft working version (BP)
	
Version 0.1 -- 1999-05-27 (BP)
----------------------------

- Directory structure created by pkgmaker.

